  <TITLE>Support for JSON messages</TITLE>
  <DESCRIPTION>I was wondering if there was any possibility of adding support for messages in formats beyond just Avro/Base64. For my use case (and likely many others), only strings are passed back and forth, so encoding to Base64 seems like overkill. Having to encode in Base64 isn't a huge pain point, but just seems unnecessary. Apologies if this is already supported and I just didn't find it in the documentation since I just started working with this today! Looks like it will be quite useful regardless. :)</DESCRIPTION>
